snippet.title: 12 Times Johnny Depp Tried To Warn Us About Amber Heard | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
12 Times Johnny Depp Tried To Warn Us About Amber Heard | Celebrity Craze

The Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp saga continues!

Johnny Depp has had a pretty interesting life the last few years. It has been funny, happy, and sad. Likely due to his current  long and rigorous court case with his ex wife. 

This court case is calling Johnny Depp's character into question. He continues to fight for his life and reputation. To show to prove that he isn’t what the media and others make him out to be. 

If you paid attention during certain points in his life during the past few years, he has sent slight warnings on what was happening to him. But you may not have realized it.
